response.original_title: HORSE the band: The Effing 69 World Tour
response.overview: On July 5, 2004, HORSE the band embarked on an incredible 12 week journey - what would soon become known as "The Effing 69 Tour." Even though, in the end, no one actually 69ed over the course of these 84 days, a disproportionate amount of a**l play took place and was thankfully captured on video.  Experience first=-hand what it's like to BE in H the B. Watch them eat, drink, lurk, and party - adding meaning to your piece of crap life by living vicariously through your favorite band.
response.title: HORSE the band: The Effing 69 World Tour
